---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title="About — Home Theory" description="Why we built Home Theory and what it's for." />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1 class="title">About Home Theory</h1>
			<p class="p">Home Theory started as a side project born out of a very ordinary problem. We kept getting asked the same questions by friends and family — can a PR buy BTO with a Singaporean spouse, what happens if you're widowed and want to buy alone, how much grant money are we actually eligible for — and we kept giving different answers each time, because the rules are genuinely complicated and scattered across a dozen different HDB pages.</p>
			<p class="p">We decided the better answer wasn't to keep explaining it one conversation at a time — it was to build something that gets it right once and gets it right for everyone. So we built a tool that asks the questions properly, applies the actual rules correctly, and tells you exactly what you qualify for — no guessing, no outdated forum advice, no sales pitch.</p>
			<p class="p">Home Theory is still small, but our team checks the rules against HDB directly, and we're building it the way we'd want it built if we were the ones trying to figure out our own eligibility at midnight before a big decision.</p>
			<p class="p closing">If you're trying to make sense of what you can actually buy, that's exactly who we built this for. Try the quiz, or browse our guides — and if something's unclear or you spot an error, we genuinely want to hear about it.</p>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>

<style>
	* {
		box-sizing: border-box;
	}
	main {
		width: 100%;
		max-width: 760px;
		padding: 60px 40px 100px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}
	.title {
		font-family: Georgia, serif;
		font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 42px);
		font-weight: 700;
		color: #1C1A17;
		margin: 0 0 32px;
	}
	.p {
		font-size: 16px;
		color: #3A3733;
		line-height: 1.7;
		margin: 0 0 22px;
	}
	.closing {
		color: #5A5040;
		font-style: italic;
	}
</style>